                            <comment id="13256160" author="thepaul" created="Wed, 18 Apr 2012 02:55:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry, should have been more specific. This is not cqlsh related; it causes an NPE in the Cassandra server:&lt;/p&gt;

